# 环境变量配置模板

## 后端环境变量 (backend/.env)

### Vercel 部署
```env
# 数据库 (可使用 Vercel Postgres 或 MongoDB Atlas)
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/price-comparison
REDIS_URL=rediss://username:password@redis_HOST.redis.cloud.redislabs.com

# 服务器
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=production
FRONTEND_URL=https://your-project.vercel.app

# JWT
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-change-in-production
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# 爬虫配置
PUPPETEER_HEADLESS=true
SCRAPER_TIMEOUT=30000
SCRAPER_RETRY_COUNT=3

# 平台配置
MEITUAN_BASE_URL=https://hotel.meituan.com
CTRIP_BASE_URL=https://www.ctrip.com
FLIGGY_BASE_URL=https://www.fliggy.com

# 缓存配置
CACHE_TTL=3600
CACHE_PREFIX=price-comparison

# 日志
LOG_LEVEL=info
```

### Cloudflare Workers 部署
```env
# Cloudflare D1 (SQLite)
DB=your-d1-database-id

# Cloudflare KV
PRICE_CACHE=your-kv-namespace-id

# 其他配置相同
```

---

## 前端环境变量 (frontend/.env.local)

### Vercel 部署
```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-project.vercel.app/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL=wss://your-project.vercel.app
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://your-project.vercel.app
```

### Cloudflare Pages 部署
```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://hotel-flight-price-comparison-api.workers.dev/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL=wss://hotel-flight-price-comparison-api.workers.dev
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://hotel-flight-price-comparison.pages.dev
```

---
